    <title>MySQL Where子句</title>
    <link href="/2021/09/10/MySQL%20Where%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5/"/>
    <url>/2021/09/10/MySQL%20Where%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%A5/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MySQL-Where子句"><a href="#MySQL-Where子句" class="headerlink" title="MySQL Where子句"></a>MySQL Where子句</h1><h2 id="用途："><a href="#用途：" class="headerlink" title="用途："></a>用途：</h2><br><blockquote><p>用於條件判斷，過濾資料</p></blockquote><br><h2 id="語法："><a href="#語法：" class="headerlink" title="語法："></a>語法：</h2><br><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span><br>..<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <br>    表格名 <br><span class="hljs-keyword">where</span> <br>    條件<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><h3 id="比較運算子"><a href="#比較運算子" class="headerlink" title="比較運算子"></a>比較運算子</h3><br><table><thead><tr><th align="center">運算元</th><th align="center">語意</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">=</td><td align="center">等於</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">&gt;</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">&gt;=</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">&lt;</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">&lt;=</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">!=</td></tr></tbody></table><br><h3 id="邏輯運算子"><a href="#邏輯運算子" class="headerlink" title="邏輯運算子"></a>邏輯運算子</h3><br><table><thead><tr><th align="center">運算元</th><th align="center">語意</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">and</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">or</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">not</td></tr></tbody></table><br><h3 id="SQL-特定運算子"><a href="#SQL-特定運算子" class="headerlink" title="SQL 特定運算子"></a>SQL 特定運算子</h3><br><table><thead><tr><th align="center">運算元</th><th align="center">語意</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">between 值1 and 值2</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">in(值1, .., 值N)</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">like</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">is null</td></tr></tbody></table><br><h3 id="Like-模糊比對"><a href="#Like-模糊比對" class="headerlink" title="Like 模糊比對"></a>Like 模糊比對</h3><br><table><thead><tr><th align="center">運算元</th><th align="center">語意</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">%</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">_</td></tr><tr><td align="center"></td><td align="center">escape</td></tr></tbody></table><br><p>範例：</p><br><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs SQL">ENAME <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;%w%&#x27;</span>→ 含有w <br>ENAME <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;w%&#x27;</span> → w開頭 <br>ENAME <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;%w&#x27;</span> → w結尾<br><br>ENAME <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;_w_&#x27;</span> → 第<span class="hljs-number">2</span>個字元為w，且ENAME長度為<span class="hljs-number">3</span> <br>ENAME <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;_w&#x27;</span> → 第<span class="hljs-number">2</span>個字元為w，且ENAME長度為<span class="hljs-number">2</span> <br>ENAME <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;w_l%&#x27;</span> → w開頭，第<span class="hljs-number">3</span>字元為l<br><br>TEXT <span class="hljs-keyword">like</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;100/%%&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">escape</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span> → <span class="hljs-number">100</span><span class="hljs-operator">%</span>開頭<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
