    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="MySQL-Select子句"><a href="#MySQL-Select子句" class="headerlink" title="MySQL Select子句"></a>MySQL Select子句</h1><h2 id="用途："><a href="#用途：" class="headerlink" title="用途："></a>用途：</h2><br><ul><li>用以查詢Table內的資料</li><li>僅查詢，不會改變資料</li></ul><br><h2 id="語法："><a href="#語法：" class="headerlink" title="語法："></a>語法：</h2><br><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> &#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">distinct</span>&#125;<br>    欄位名<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, .., 欄位名N<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span>    <br>    表格名;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>若 select 子句後面加上 distinct 及顯示不重複資料</p></blockquote><br><h3 id="字串串接"><a href="#字串串接" class="headerlink" title="字串串接"></a>字串串接</h3><br><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <br>    CONCAT( 字串<span class="hljs-number">1</span>, 字串<span class="hljs-number">2</span>, 字串<span class="hljs-number">3</span>, ... )<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span>    <br>    表格名;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>將欄位內的值 或 字面常數做串接</p></blockquote><br><h3 id="case運算式"><a href="#case運算式" class="headerlink" title="case運算式"></a>case運算式</h3><br><ul><li>列舉式(Simple Case)</li></ul><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span> 欄位名 <span class="hljs-operator">|</span> 運算式 <span class="hljs-operator">|</span> 字面常數 <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">when</span> 列舉值<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span> 結果<span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>        ..<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">when</span> 列舉值N <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span> 結果N<br>        &#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> 結果&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">end</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span>   表格名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><ul><li>條件式(Searched Case)</li></ul><figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs sql"><span class="hljs-keyword">select</span> <br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">case</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">when</span> 條件<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span> 結果<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <br>        ..<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">when</span> 條件N <span class="hljs-keyword">then</span> 結果N<br>        &#123;<span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> 結果&#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">end</span>  <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> &#123;一般會加上表格名&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span>   表格名<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
